11#ifndef MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_DECODER_DATABASE_H_
12#define MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_DECODER_DATABASE_H_
13
14#include <map>
15#include <memory>
16
17#include "modules/video_coding/generic_decoder.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21struct VCMDecoderMapItem {
22 public:
23 VCMDecoderMapItem(VideoCodec* settings, int number_of_cores);
24 ~VCMDecoderMapItem();
25
26 std::unique_ptr<VideoCodec> settings;
27 int number_of_cores;
28};
29
30struct VCMExtDecoderMapItem {
31 public:
32 VCMExtDecoderMapItem(VideoDecoder* external_decoder_instance,
33 uint8_t payload_type);
34
35 uint8_t payload_type;
36 VideoDecoder* external_decoder_instance;
37};
38
39class VCMDecoderDataBase {
40 public:
41 VCMDecoderDataBase();
42 ~VCMDecoderDataBase();
43
44 bool DeregisterExternalDecoder(uint8_t payload_type);
45 void RegisterExternalDecoder(VideoDecoder* external_decoder,
46 uint8_t payload_type);
47 bool IsExternalDecoderRegistered(uint8_t payload_type) const;
48
49 bool RegisterReceiveCodec(uint8_t payload_type,
50 const VideoCodec* receive_codec,
51 int number_of_cores);
52 bool DeregisterReceiveCodec(uint8_t payload_type);
53
54 // Returns a decoder specified by frame.PayloadType. The decoded frame
55 // callback of the decoder is set to |decoded_frame_callback|. If no such
56 // decoder already exists an instance will be created and initialized.
57 // nullptr is returned if no decoder with the specified payload type was found
58 // and the function failed to create one.
59 VCMGenericDecoder* GetDecoder(
60 const VCMEncodedFrame& frame,
61 VCMDecodedFrameCallback* decoded_frame_callback);
62
63 private:
64 typedef std::map<uint8_t, VCMDecoderMapItem*> DecoderMap;
65 typedef std::map<uint8_t, VCMExtDecoderMapItem*> ExternalDecoderMap;
66
67 std::unique_ptr<VCMGenericDecoder> CreateAndInitDecoder(
68 const VCMEncodedFrame& frame,
69 VideoCodec* new_codec) const;
70
71 const VCMDecoderMapItem* FindDecoderItem(uint8_t payload_type) const;
72
73 const VCMExtDecoderMapItem* FindExternalDecoderItem(
74 uint8_t payload_type) const;
75
76 uint8_t current_payload_type_; // Corresponding to receive_codec_.
77 VideoCodec receive_codec_;
78 std::unique_ptr<VCMGenericDecoder> ptr_decoder_;
79 DecoderMap dec_map_;
80 ExternalDecoderMap dec_external_map_;
81};
82
83} // namespace webrtc
84
85#endif // MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_DECODER_DATABASE_H_
